465
00:43:15,954 --> 00:43:18,287
<font color="#ffff00">Dùng góc đẹp đó, Charles à.</font>

466
00:43:18,289 --> 00:43:21,207
<font color="#ffff00">- Được rồi, Charlie Brown.
